txt.en: 'It appears the Ungoledain have already been spotted heading towards Rushgate. We can't be sure if this was a small group of them or if their ranks are in far greater numbers to the west.\n\n'Track the Ungoledain, [placeholder]. Do not engage them though, if you can avoid it. They are in retreat and we want to keep an eye on them to see what they plan next.'
